pageContext.claim: “‘On February 19th there was a Democratic Debate, in Las Vegas. Three words weren't said: Virus, CoronaVirus, or COVID19. NEVER came up!’ @BretBaier”
pageContext.analysis: Yes, but here's the missing context: The United States had 13 confirmed coronavirus cases at the time and the lethargic response to the outbreak from the Trump administration had not yet been reported.
